{"tid":1655463,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【10.19全城反共文宣日】連儂牆要一個個主題咁貼！連儂牆進化～赤納角！","createTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T07:12:16.000Z","uid":117906,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"dfcd89ab9bc3afbe79bcb0a26f9503219cae8d4b","tid":1655463,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>以後連儂牆唔再係一張張A4咁貼！ <br />\n要一個一個主題咁貼！好似赤納角咁！<br />\n全城反共 連儂牆進化～赤納角！<br />\n反共專欄，專門記載Chinazi惡行</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">第一期專題：赤色資本入侵世界</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">全套赤納角文宣圖放左係#2<br />\n或者去呢到拎 -＞ <a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazicorner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazicorner&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=ef442fb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazicorner</a> <br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月十九日 貼滿成個香港！</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kayPpvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkayPpvg.png&h=5620fbfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xJLDBj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xJLDBj.png&h=5ab63c11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PowhuHn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPowhuHn.jpg&h=51b83262&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>21世紀既香港再次身負重任成為革命基地！<br />\n用反共文宣屌醒班置身事外既港豬！<br />\n用反共文宣輸出反共革命！點醒外國人，共匪就黎吞拼全世界！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n抗爭已經4個月<br />\n面對港共既無恥、傲慢；黑警既濫捕、暴力<br />\n可能有時候我地會灰心、迷失、沮喪<br />\n<br />\n但同時大家睇得好清楚：<br />\n港共勾結中共勢力 企圖將香港赤化 令人髪指<br />\n<br />\n去到今時今日 <br />\n香港人既敵人已經唔再係反送中<br />\n香港人既訴求亦唔單單係五大訴求<br />\n香港人既口號亦進化成「香港人反抗！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我地既最終敵人 一直都係中共</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>若果你尚有猶疑：問自己一句，中共信唔信得過？</strong></span><br />\n<strong>對準政權 抗共求存</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nsfYYFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnsfYYFJ.png&h=fc135546&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<strong>🔥<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要人！想幫手：</span> <a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazihk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazihk&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=e96b1517\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazihk</a></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">1。資料搜集： 共匪所有罪行既資料<br />\n2。文宣設計<br />\n3。翻譯：同步變埋做英文，國際線材料</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【赤納角圖書館】</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>我地同時建造緊TG共匪罪行大全！好需要大家幫手資料搜集！(報料去以下bot)</strong><br />\n入黎參觀圖書館： <a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazihk/8432\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazihk%2F8432&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=8be53bc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazihk/8432</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【長期抗共】反赤納粹新聞、文宣、投稿收集Bot</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazicollect_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazicollect_bot&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=1f918599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazicollect_bot</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【長期抗共】反赤納粹新聞、文宣、投稿整合發佈Channel</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazichannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazichannel&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=88b51104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazichannel</a></strong><br />\n-"},{"pid":"fda8ae97e40001430f6ef17befca456612e93c40","tid":1655463,"uid":117906,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T05:30:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">赤納角 連儂牆材料包 <a href=\"http://t.me/antichinazicorner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fantichinazicorner&d=P9V%2Fg5HR%2BYIczjwvlITT9K9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=ef442fb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/antichinazicorner</a><br />\n以後連儂牆唔再係一張張A4咁貼！ <br />\n全城反共 以後要一個一個主題咁貼！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4xJLDBj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4xJLDBj.png&h=5ab63c11&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZjYjH2X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZjYjH2X.png&h=f173f8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XU5J9HX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXU5J9HX.png&h=e7d60dee&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2SqewWi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2SqewWi.png&h=85b5994f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/meRQPHT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmeRQPHT.png&h=649a36e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C88jH2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC88jH2S.png&h=bedc85cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZCjZH2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCjZH2T.png&h=d9ea0350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cj8vPHV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcj8vPHV.png&h=a796af10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i